==Trivia==
*Dr Jekyll is a direct reference to the mystery novel ''[[Wikipedia:Strange Case of Dr Jekyll and Mr Hyde|Strange Case of Dr Jekyll and Mr Hyde]]'' by Robert Louis Stevenson. It is about a doctor who created a potion, splitting himself into two distinct personalities. He existed as the kind, gentle Dr Jekyll, and the fearsome, malevolent Mr Hyde.
*If a player receives this random event underwater, Jekyll will be seen wearing diving gear.

